        </a>
        <h2>
            菜根谭（全四册）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 2 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5270764">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5270764/" class="title-link">自己的书就是看得慢啊</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5270764"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2511344/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2511344-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2511344/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">花缸思忒2</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-16"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-16 09:17:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5270764_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书非借不可读啊， 自己买的《菜根谭》这本书， 看了好久才看完， 最后都看得有点闷了， 以后还是多借书看吧。  菜根谭不适合年轻人看， 没有富贵过怎么知道应该不骄奢， 没有成功过怎么知道应该不骄傲。 还在穷困的时候怎么去骄奢？ 还在卑贱的时候骄傲给谁看？ 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5270764/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5270764_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5270764_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2755670">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
